'Yan majalisar dokokin Wales sun damu da yin kama da ' yan tsana
Wasu 'yan majalisa ba su yarda da shawarar cewa dole ne a canza sunan zuwa UPM (ɗan majalisar dokokin Wales) ba.
Wannan batun ya taso ne saboda shirin canza sunan majalisa zuwa majalisar dokokin Wales.
Suna tsoron cewa sunan memba na majalisar zai zama abin dariya a duk faɗin yankin siyasa.
Wani memba na majalisar ya ce yana damuwa da cewa kungiyar 'yan Labour ta yi amfani da kalmomin ol Twp da Pwp.
Ga masu karatu a waje da Wales: a cikin yaren Welsh, twp  yana nufin jin da pwp nageis.
Wani memba na majalisar jam'iyyar Welsh ya ce kungiyar ba ta da 'yancin yin amfani da shi, kuma ya gabatar da wasu hanyoyin.
Wani mai kula da Wales ya lura cewa ƙungiyar ta kasance mai sauƙin canza sunan, amma yana da bambanci kaɗan a cikin yadda ake furta tsakanin kalmomin MWP da Muppet.
Wannan rubutun yana da irin wannan furcin haruffan Welsh w kamar yadda yake da haruffan Yorkshire Turanci.
Don gabatar da canje-canjen suna, hukumar majalisar da ke shirya lissafin a halin yanzu ta ce: Sanarwar ƙarshe game da wasu fasalulluka game da yadda ake kiran membobin majalisar, ba shakka, membobin za su yanke shawara da kansu.
A cewar Dokar Gwamnatin Wales ta 2017, Majalisar Wales ta sami damar canza sunanta.
A watan Yuni, Hukumar ta sanar da sakamakon taron jama'a game da shawarwari da suka sami babban goyon baya ga kiran majalisar a matsayin 'yan majalisar Wales'.
Game da sunan 'yan majalisa, Hukumar ta fi son sunan 'yan majalisar dokokin Wales' ko 'yan majalisar WMP, amma a taron jama'a yawancin sun goyi bayan 'yan majalisar WMP.
Koyaya, membobin Majalisar suna ba da zaɓuɓɓuka na daban, amma gwagwarmayar da shugaban Hukumar, Elaine Jones, wanda ake tsammanin zai gabatar da ƙirar doka game da canje-canje a cikin 'yan makonni, na iya haifar da wasu matsaloli.
Dokar ta ƙunshi wasu canje-canje ga tsarin aiki na majalisar, da kuma ka'idodin ƙin yarda da mambobi na Majalisar da kuma tsarin kwamiti.
Bayan da 'yan majalisa suka tattauna batun, za su yanke shawarar yadda za a kira shi.
