Bayan da Holly Willoughby ta yi watsi da yarjejeniyar fam miliyan 11 , Peter Jones ya fusata
Bayan da mai gabatar da shirye-shiryen talabijin Holly Willoughby ya soke yarjejeniyarta na miliyan 11 da alamar rayuwarta don tara sabbin yarjejeniyoyinta da Marks da Spencer da kuma ITV, Peter Jones, tauraron shirin Dragons Den ya fusata 
Willoughby ba shi da lokaci don yin amfani da kayan ado da kayan haɗi na gida.
Wannan ma'aurata suna da alaƙa da Gwyneth Paltrow's Goop brand.
A safiyar yau, mai gabatar da shirye-shiryen talabijin mai shekaru 37 ya rubuta cewa zai tafi shafinsa na Instagram.
Don ba da ƙarin haske ga yarjejeniyar Holly Willowby da Marks & Spencer da kuma ITV, tauraron shirin Dragons Den ya yanke shawarar barin kasuwancin Peter Jones mai nasara na alamar rayuwa a cikin lokaci na ƙarshe, yana sanya shi cikin mawuyacin hali.
A wani taron da aka yi a babban ofishin kamfanin a garin Marlow, Buckinghamshire, a ranar Talata, lokacin da 'yar gidan talabijin ta amince cewa sabon yarjejeniyar da ta kai fam miliyan 1.5 na nufin ba su da lokacin tallata kayan gida da kayan haɗi na Truly, Jones ya ce ya fusata.
Wannan kasuwancin ya danganta da Gvinette Paltrow's Goop brand kuma zai iya ninka matsayin Willowby wanda ya kai fam miliyan 11.
A lokacin da Willowby ya kai shekara 37, ya shiga shafin Instagram don sanar da cewa zai bar Truly, Jones ya tashi daga United Kingdom zuwa ɗayan gidajen hutu.
Kafofin watsa labarai sun ce: A gaskiya, Truly ba shine abin da Holly ke nufi ba.
Wannan shi ne abin da zai faru a nan gaba, shekaru da dama bayan haka.
Shawarwarin da ya yi na fita daga wasan ya kawo matsala ga duk 'yan wasan.
Ba wanda zai gaskata abin da ya faru a ranar Talata, domin ranar tana kusa.
Babban ofishin a gundumar Marlow yana da shago mai cike da kayayyaki masu sayarwa.
Masana sun yi imanin cewa tafiyar mai gudanar da This Morning, wanda ya kasance daya daga cikin taurari mafiya yawan biyan kuɗi a Burtaniya, zai iya haifar da asarar miliyoyin kuɗi ga kamfanin saboda babban gudummawa ga kayan aiki, daga kayan ado da fitilu, da kayan gida, da kuma yiwuwar jinkirta ƙaddamar da shi.
Hakan kuma zai iya nufin cewa abokantaka ta daɗe sosai.
Willowby, mahaifiyar yara uku, da matarsa Dan Baldwin sun kasance cikin dangantaka mai kyau da Johnson da matarsa Tara Cap na tsawon shekaru 10.
Willowby ya kafa kamfanin Truly tare da Cap a shekara ta 2016, kuma Jones, mai shekaru 52, ya shiga matsayin shugaban a watan Maris.
Ma'aurata suna yin hutu tare kuma suna da kashi 40 cikin dari na kamfanin talabijin na Jones Baldwin.
Willowby yana shirin zama jakadan M&S kuma zai maye gurbin Anth McPartlin, mai gabatar da shirin I'm A Celebrity a kan tashar ITV.
Wani mutum da ke da alaka da Jones a daren jiya ya ce, "Ba mu da wata sanarwa game da ayyukan da ke tattare da kasuwancinsa".
