Kocin Lakers, Luke Walton, ya sanar da cewa zai buga wasan da James Denver a ranar Lahadi a wasan bude kakar wasa a San Diego.
Za mu ga nawa minti zai iya wasa.
"Da yawa, fiye da 48", Walton ya ce a shafin yanar gizon Lakers.
Wani mai rahoto na Lakers, Mike Traddle, ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa James zai iya yin wasan na iyakantaccen lokaci.
Bayan atisayen wannan makon, an nemi James ya yi wasa game da jadawalin wasanni shida na Lakers.
Ta ce ba na bukatar wasanni na kakar wasa don shirya kaina a wannan lokacin na rayuwa.
Gasar Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaban kasa Donald Trump zai kaddamar da taron jama'a a birnin Wheeling, West Virginia a daren yau.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin tarurrukan Trump guda biyar da za a yi a wannan makon, idan aka lissafa wuraren da za su tsaya a wurare masu haɗin gwiwa kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yayin da yake jiran a tabbatar da dan takararsa a Kotun Koli, Trump zai kara yawan magoya bayan zaben ta gaba saboda Republican na cikin hadarin rasa goyon bayan Majalisar a lokacin zaben a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump zai fara a yammacin yau a birnin Wheeling, West Virginia, kuma ta yaya za ku iya kallon shi a kan layi?
Ana sa ran taron Trump na gabanin zaben zai fara ne a Wheeling, West Virginia, da karfe 7 na yamma, ranar Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon zaben Trump a West Virginia ta hanyar hanyar YouTube ta hanyar hanyar haɗin kai tsaye a ƙasa.
Trump zai yi magana game da sauraron da ake yi a wannan makon na dan takarar Kotun Koli, Brett Kavanao, wanda ya haifar da muhawara mai zafi cewa Majalisar Dattawa ta jinkirta karar ta mako guda kafin FBI ta kammala binciken.
Amma babban burin wannan gwagwarmayar na gaba da zaben shine taimakawa 'yan Republican su tabbatar da matsayinsu kafin zaben na Nuwamba.
Saboda haka, taron shugaban kasa na Trump guda biyar da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa zai ƙarfafa masu neman agaji da magoya baya, saboda Republican suna ƙoƙarin karewa da kuma karɓar rinjaye a Majalisar Dattijai da ƙananan majalisa, in ji Reuters.
"Sauye-sauyen da ake yi a kan majalisa yana da muhimmanci sosai, saboda haka shugaban kasa zai yi ƙoƙari ya ziyarci jihohi da yawa kamar yadda zai yiwu kafin lokacin zaɓen", in ji wani mai magana da yawun Trump, wanda ya yi watsi da bayyana sunansa ga Reuters.
A cikin yammacin taron da za a yi a Wessbanco Arena a Wheeling, magoya bayan Ohio da Pennsylvania na iya halartar taron, wanda ba shakka zai sami hankalin kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh a tashar West Virginia Metro News.
Wannan shi ne karo na biyu da Trump zai ziyarci West Virginia a ranar Asabar tun watan da ya gabata, kuma ya lashe zaben ne a jihar da ta samu kashi 40 cikin 100 na kuri'un da aka kada a shekarar 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa dan takarar majalisar dattijai ta West Virginia, Patrick Morrissey, wanda ya rage a zaben.
"Ba shi da kyau ga Morrissey cewa shugaban kasa ya zo don ya kara masa karfin gwiwa a zabensa", in ji Simon Heather, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia.
Ryder Cup 2018: 'Yan wasan Amurka sun nuna cewa suna shirye su yi gwagwarmaya don cin nasara kafin wasannin da za a yi a ranar Lahadi
Bayan an kammala wasanni uku na tseren ƙofa guda, hudu da suka sake yin wasa a ranar Asabar da yamma sun shiga gasar Ryder Cup.
Fuskar fanfo hanya ce mai kyau ta wasanni, amma masu wasa suna da babban fata a irin wannan gasa.
Tambayar ita ce, ina ne wannan yanayin yake faruwa?
"Suna da maki shida a gaba, yanzu muna da maki hudu, kuma ina tsammanin muna da sauri", Jordan Spit ya ce a lokacin da yake dawowa a ranar.
