Turai ta shiga wasan karshe na gasar cin kofin Ryder da ci 10-6
Turai ta yi rashin nasara a wasan karshe na gasar cin kofin Ryder bayan ta fi Amurka 10-6 bayan buga kwallo hudu da kuma wasan hudu a ranar Asabar.
Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari, ma'aurata masu ban mamaki, sun ci Tiger Woods biyu, kuma sun ci Le Golf National da maki hudu.
