Geiger ya kirkiro hanyar ganowa da kuma auna radiation, wanda ya zama na'urar da aka kira Geiger calculator.
Daga nan Geiger ya zama tushen al'adun gargajiya, kamar yadda yake a cikin fim din Coronado Bell din 1950, wanda ya kasance mai yawanci masu bincike na yau da kullum Roy Rogers da Dale Evans:
Mutum: Mecece wannan al'ada?
Rogers:  Wannan shi ne mai lissafin Geiger wanda aka yi amfani da shi don gano ma'adanai masu radiation kamar uranium.
