Ronaldo ya ki amincewa da karar da ake masa na fyade saboda masu kare shi sun yi tunanin cewa zai mika mujallar Jamus ga kotu
Cristiano Ronaldo ya bayyana zargin da ake masa na fyade a matsayin "bayanan karya", kuma mutane sun ce suna amfani da sunansa don "sake bayyana sunayensu".
Masu kare shi sun yi niyyar kai wa kotu mujallar jaridar Der Spiegel, wadda ta sanar da zargin.
An zargi wani dan wasan Portugal da Juventus da yin fyade da wata mata 'yar Amurka mai suna Catherine Majorga a wani otal a Las Vegas a shekarar 2009.
A wata sanarwa da jaridar Der Spiegel ta fitar a ranar Juma'a, ta ce ta biya shi dala 375,000 domin kada a bayyana cewa lamarin ya faru.
Bayan 'yan sa'o'i bayan karbar sanarwar, Ronaldo mai shekara 33 ya bayyana cewa sanarwar "bayanan karya" ne a cikin wani bidiyo da ya yi a shafinsa na Instagram a gaban masu biyan kuɗi miliyan 142.
