Wannan al'amari ne na al'ada.
Suna so su yi suna da sunana, kuma wannan shi ne aikinsu.
Ni mutum ne mai farin ciki kuma ina da kyau".
A cewar Reuters, masu kare Ronaldo suna shirin kai karar da suka yi wa jaridar Der Spiegel a matsayin "ba a gafarta musu ba game da zargin sirri".
Mai kare Kristian Schertz ya ce mai kunnawa zai buƙaci biyan diyya "daidai da girman lalacewar da aka yi, wanda ya zama ɗayan mafi munin nau'ikan keta haƙƙin mutum a cikin 'yan shekarun nan".
An samu rahoton cewa wannan lamarin ya faru ne a wani otal a Palms Hotel and Casino a Las Vegas a watan Yuni na shekarar 2009.
Takardun da aka gabatar zuwa Kotun Yankin Clark a Nevada sun nuna cewa bayan ganawar da suka yi a gidan wasan dare, Ronaldo da Majorca sun koma ɗakin dan wasan kuma a can ya yi mata fyade.
Bayan wannan babban abin da ya faru, Majorga ya ce Ronaldo ya durƙusa ya gaya masa cewa "kashi 99 cikin dari" na "kyakkyawan saurayi" ne kuma ya "shiga kashi ɗaya cikin dari".
Kamar yadda takardun suka nuna, Ronaldo ya ce ma'auratan sun yi jima'i da juna ta hanyar yarjejeniya.
A cewar Majorga, ta kai ga 'yan sanda kuma ta yi hotunan raunukan da ta samu a asibiti, amma daga baya ta yanke shawarar magance lamarin a waje da kotu saboda tsoron "tabbatarwa" da "tsanani a gaban jama'a".
Idan muka yi imani da maganar matashi mai shekaru 34, har yanzu yana shan wahala saboda abin da ya faru, saboda haka ba ya son tsayawa a wani wuri.
