Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
A ranar Juma'a, girgizar kasa da tsunami da suka auku a birnin Pallu na Indonesia sun kashe mutane 384, kuma jami'an kasar sun ce, ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Saboda katsewar sadarwa, ma'aikatan cibiyoyin agaji ba su iya samun wani bayani daga yankin Donggala a arewacin garin Palú ba, wanda ke kusa da yanayin girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi 7.5.
Bayan bala'in a Palau, an kwashe mutane sama da 16,000.
Ga wasu bayanai game da Palau da Donggala a Sulawesi:
Palo ita ce babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya kuma tana kan gabar yamma ta tsibirin Sulawesi, a ƙarshen bakin teku, yawan jama'a a shekara ta 2017 ya kai kimanin 379,800.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka shafa, birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da haihuwa.
Donggala wani yanki ne na arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi wanda ya fi kilomita 300 (180 mil) a gefen tekun.
A cikin ƙananan yankunan lardin, yawan mazaunan yankin ya kai 299,200 a shekarar 2017.
Kifi da noma sune tushen tattalin arzikin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, musamman yankin bakin teku na Donggala.
Har ila yau, yin nickel yana da mahimmanci a lardin, amma sana'ar ta kasance a Moravia, a kan iyakar Sulawesi.
Hukumar kula da bala'i ta Indonesia ta ruwaito cewa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, tsunami ya faru sau da yawa a Palau da Donggala.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya halaka mutane fiye da 200 a yankin Donggala kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje.
Tsunami ya rushe yankin yammacin Donggala a 1996, inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake kira "Ruwa ta Pacific" saboda an yi ta fama da girgizar kasa.
Wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka faru a cikin ' yan shekarun nan sun haɗa da:
2004: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a kan tekun yamma na lardin Aceh, a arewacin tsibirin Sumatra, Indonesia, a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, ta haifar da tsunami a ƙasashe 14, wanda ya haifar da mutuwar mutane 226,000 a gabar Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: A ƙarshen watan Nuwamba da farkon Afrilu, an yi girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a yammacin tsibirin Sumatra.
Kuma ɗaruruwan mutane suka mutu a tsibirin Ni'ash, a bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin maki 6.8 ta afku a tsibirin Java, wanda ke kudu maso gabashin Indonesia, inda ta kai ga bakin teku na kudu, inda ta kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.6 ta afku a Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 sun mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.5 a tsibirin Metawai a Sumatra ta haifar da tsunami mai tsawon mita 10, wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da dama, ya kashe kusan mutane 300.
2016: A cikin yankin Pidi-Jay na Aceh, girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarancin ƙarfi ta haifar da rikice-rikice da tashin hankali a cikin al'umma, saboda an yi gargadin mutane game da mummunan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a shekara ta 2004.
A wannan lokacin, babu tsunami, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu a ƙarƙashin gine-gine da suka rushe.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na yawon buɗe ido na Indonesia, inda sama da mutane 500 suka mutu a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ƙasa ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta hana dubban masu yawon buɗe ido komawa gidajensu na ɗan lokaci.
